[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あ、レスナちゃんだ！　おーい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00279",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃんにヨハナちゃん、鬼門ちゃん！\n三人揃ってどうしたの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00280",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "明後日の２ｎｄライブに向けて、\n宣伝のためのビラ配り中なのでございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00281",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はい。ライブ観に来なさいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00282",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうございます！\n絶対行きますっ！　最前列で見ますっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00283",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あ、暑苦しいわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00284",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "す、すみません！　昨日の皆さんのライブを\n見てから、次のライブがすっごく楽しみで……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00285",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "他のアイドルのライブ動画とか見て、\n盛り上がる練習もしました！　掛け声も完璧です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00286",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "なんとっ！　レスナ殿は真面目ですな。\n拙者もコールアンドレスポンスを用意しておかねば",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00287",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "二人ともバカ真面目ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00288",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "あっ、そういえば、\n色々なライブ動画を見ていて思ったんですが――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00289",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "ライブで花火とか、紙吹雪とかの派手な演出を\n入れるのはどうでしょうか！　盛り上がると思います！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00290",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "紙吹雪は忍術でできまするが、後片付けが……\n花火は火薬が危ないですし、音の問題もあって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00291",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "実はその問題、錬金術で全部解決できちゃいます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00292",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "な、なんとっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00293",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "錬金術なら、音がない花火も、熱くない花火も、\n溶けて消える紙吹雪なんかも作れちゃうんです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00294",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "すごい！　それがあれば、\nもっとライブが盛り上がりそうだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00295",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃんが頑張ってるから、私も錬金術で\n何か協力できないかなって思ったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00296",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "レスナちゃん……！　ありがとー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00297",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "レスナの申し出はありがたいけれど、\nそれはあんた一人で決めていいことなの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00298",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "実は先ほど、そこで先輩や先生方を見つけたので、\n今から相談しに行こうと思っていたんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00299",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "先輩に協力をお願いできたら、百人力ですから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00300",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それじゃあ、一緒に行こう！\nチラシも渡したいし！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00301",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "うん！　みんなで行こう！　やーっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00302",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]